# Skill: project-tracker

## Purpose
Keep project files current. Surface status, blockers, and next actions.

## Files

- projects/index.md — overview table
- projects/[name].md — detail per project

## Rules

- Every project in the index needs a detail file
- Status: Not started / In progress / On hold / Complete
- Blockers must be updated every touch — "None" is valid
- Next action must be specific and owned

## Weekly review (every Friday)

- What progressed?
- What is stale (7+ days untouched)?
- What blockers need attention?

## Adding a project

1. Create projects/[name].md from template.md
2. Add row to projects/index.md
3. Add next action to tasks/current.md
